Class UserDetails

java.lang.Object
com.atu.green_global_initiative_api.model.dao.UserDetails
@Entity public class UserDetails extends Object
Represents the user details in the Green Global Initiative application system. This class contains the user's personal information, credentials, admin status, last login details, and their associated application details.
